'''維道古律斯站'''（{{lang-tl|Estasyon ng Vito Cruz}}）位在[[馬尼拉|馬尼拉]]{{link-en|馬拉提區|Malate, Manila}}，屬於[[馬尼拉輕軌|馬尼拉輕軌]][[馬尼拉輕軌1號線|1號線]]的車站，於1984年12月1日正式啟用。該車站鄰近{{link-en|塔夫脱大道|Taft Avenue}}和{{link-en|帕布羅·奧坎波街|Pablo Ocampo Street}}（原名維道·古律斯街）路口，為[[馬尼拉|馬尼拉市]]{{link-en|馬拉提區|Malate, Manila}}的交通服務。

本站由於[[輕生|輕生]]事件發生率較高<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.abs-cbn.com/nation/metro-manila/08/30/12/lrt-driver-faces-raps-over-womans-suicide-police|title=LRT driver faces raps over woman's suicide: police|last=Macapagal|first=Maan|date=2012-08-30|publisher=[[ABS-CBN|ABS-CBN]]|accessdate=2019-06-27|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234339/https://news.abs-cbn.com/nation/metro-manila/08/30/12/lrt-driver-faces-raps-over-womans-suicide-police|dead-url=no}}</ref>，列車進站時設有特別速限以降低事故次數<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imoney.ph/articles/lrt-guide-philippines/|title=A Commuter’s Guide To Metro Manila’s LRT Network|last=Adrian|first=Marc|date=2019-01-18|publisher=iMoney Philippines|accessdate=2019-06-27|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118134112/https://www.imoney.ph/articles/lrt-guide-philippines/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.philstar.com/metro/2014/08/22/1360364/mrt-sets-speed-limit-trains|title=MRT sets speed limit for trains|last=Ronda|first=Rainier Allan|date=2014-08-22|publisher={{link-en|菲律賓星報|The Philippine Star}}|accessdate=2019-06-27|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112001146/https://www.philstar.com/metro/2014/08/22/1360364/mrt-sets-speed-limit-trains|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

